{
  "stem": "4361.9",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I never had much to do with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was much older than I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "At one time or another when he would see me, he would greet me very respectfully.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, I kiss your hand, miss, that sort of a thing, which was the appropriate thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was a little girl, and he was a big man, an old man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, he wasn't really old, but from my point of view.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when he heard that I came to Munich and I stayed with my cousin, he came one evening loaded with bananas.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I'd never seen a banana before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "With Coca-Cola-- I'd never seen-- I didn't even know what Coca-Cola was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I refused to drink it at first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he came with a pair of tickets to the opera house, which was half-bombed in Munich, but he managed those tickets.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he was very, very giving and very protective of me, and I always considered him as an older uncle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he took me to places and, and made things very pleasant for me while I was working at the Joint.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he was very good to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then one day, he said to me, he proposed to me marriage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he said, quote, I will be as good to you as your mother and father were, unquote.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I accepted because that's all I wanted then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I remember saying to myself, well, my big romance, I had it in my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I am-- my life is over and he's-- all I want, again, is my mother and father, and here was a man who offered me that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I continued working at the Joint when this immigration thing came in, and he had a brother here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was-- because he died many years ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
